import { Container, Box, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

function Error404() {
  return (
    <>
    <Container maxWidth="1600">
      <Box sx={{ 
        padding: '1em',
        height: 'auto', 
        textAlign: 'center',
        marginTop: '4em',
        }}>
        <Typography sx={{ 
          fontFamily: 'Shadows Into Light, cursive', 
          fontSize: '5em', 
          fontWeight: '700',
          color: 'primary.dark'}}>
            ERROR 404</Typography>
        <Typography sx={{ 
          fontFamily: 'Shadows Into Light, cursive', 
          fontSize: '3em', 
          fontWeight: '400',
          marginTop: '1em',
          color: 'primary.dark'}}>
            PAGE NOT FOUND</Typography>
        <Button variant="contained" href="/CreateRoutine" sx={{ 
          backgroundColor: 'primary.main',
          marginTop: '1em',
          fontFamily: 'Shadows Into Light, cursive', 
          fontSize: '3em', 
          fontWeight: '500',
          width: '40%',
          borderRadius: '20px',
          }}>GO BACK</Button>
        </Box>
    </Container>
  </>
  )
}

export default Error404
